              </Glosses>
              <Comments>As in the case of the translation of meanings in {D:33.312} and {D:33.313}, it may be necessary likewise to make certain semantic adjustments in the translation of κλητός[a] . For example, the phrase in {S:04500100100010} may be rendered as ‘urgently invited to be an apostle’ or even ‘summoned and commissioned to be an apostle.’</Comments>
